    <item>
      <title>据 Digi 报道，罗马尼亚将于 3 月 23 日重新举行总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/romania-to-rerun-presidential-election-on-march-23-digi-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Digi 24 援引知情人士的话称，罗马尼亚执政联盟同意于 3 月 23 日按计划重新举行总统选举，并于 4 月 6 日举行第二轮选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/romania-to-rerun-presidential-election-on-march-23-digi-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 13:29:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安称土耳其利率将在 2025 年下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/erdogan-says-turkey-interest-rates-will-definitely-fall-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安表示，2025年利率将会下降，他再次表达了自己非传统的信念，即降低利率将减缓物价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/erdogan-says-turkey-interest-rates-will-definitely-fall-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 13:21:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
